Constructs a new ParaRuncheck object.

Parameters:
pos - - the original position in the file (null if unknown)
path - - a valid path to the Unit containing the paragraph
name - - the name of the assertion (can be an empty string)
check - - true if this is a "check"; false if this is a "run".
overall - - the overall scope (-1 if no overall scope was specified)
expects - - the expected value (0 or 1) (-1 if no expectation was specified)
scope - - String-to-Integer map that maps signature name to a nonnegative scope
exact - - a set of String indicating which sigs have exact scope
Throws:
ErrorSyntax - - if name is equal to ""
ErrorSyntax - - if at least one of the signature name is ""
ErrorSyntax - - if at least one of the value in "scope" is negative
ErrorSyntax - - if at least onesignature name is in "exact" but not in "scope"
ErrorInternal - - if path==null, name==null, scope==null, or exact==null
